There are nine or ten parti|culars wherein the love of Chri&s;t to his &s;ub|jects doth appear, and is wonderfully mani|fe&s;t.
<LIST>
<ITEM>1. <HI>His love to his &s;ubjects,</HI> 'tis Primary: <HI>We love him,</HI> &s;aith the Apo&s;tle, <HI>becau&s;e he lov|ed
