<PB N="73" REF="001244_0040_0FB186CCB159F4F8">in your liberty, as you have had liber|ty for your con&s;cience it had been well: that &s;oal was never related to Cari&s;t; that &s;oul was never related to Chri&s;t: there is no obtaining the price of Happine&s;s, without running the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">ce of Happine&s;s. Oh for the Lords &s;ake, do not you begin in the &s;pirit, and end in the fl<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">&s;h. Oh do not you put your hand to the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">low, and look backward be not true to the <HI>Fa<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters"> of <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">,</HI> and fal&s;e to the <HI>God of Truth;</HI> keep clo&s;e to the Son of God, to the Word of Cod. to the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">dinances of God, to the Day of God, to the Mini&s;ters of God, to the People of God, and thou wilt be &s;afe, Gal. 6.9. <HI>Be not <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">ary i<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">ll doing, &s;<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">r in <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> &s;e<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters"> you &s;hall reap if <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">i<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">t n<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">t.</HI> I &s;hall wind up all with that &s;aying of <HI>Ig<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">tius, They who ad<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">re to them <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> ad<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">ere not to truth, &s;hall <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> inherit the Kingdom of God.<