<ITEM>9. And in their mouths w<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> found no guile; for they are without faul<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> before the throne of God. O how holy, how heavenly, how gracious, how lovely and &s;piri|tual are the&s;e; they live in the Lord, on th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> <HI>Lord,</HI> to the <HI>Lord,</HI> and with the <HI>Lord; They are <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">
