<ITEM>4. <HI>The dearly beloved of his &s;oul,</HI> Jer. 12.7.</ITEM>
<ITEM>5 <HI>God's trea&s;ure and peculiar trea&s;ure,</HI> Exod. 19.5.</ITEM>
<ITEM>6 <HI>His gl<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ry,</HI> I&s;a 46.13.</ITEM>
