<P>There is much difference between the <HI>Church</HI> of God and other men, as there is betwixt Gold and Dirt, as betwixt Diamonds and Pebbles, in the Lords e&s;teem; they are to God above all people! <HI>The righteous is more excellent than his neighbour,</HI> Prov. 12.26. O how precious, how happy, how ble&s;&s;ed and glorious are Believers? they are called Heaven.</P>
<P N="2">2. Believers are called <HI>Heaven,</HI> becau&s;e there is much of them in Heaven.</P>
